    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "A solution that I see is to have a `canRefine` function implemented on all connectors that returns a boolean based on the options (`helper`, `results`, `state`). We can then [pass it to the panel](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/v3/src/widgets/panel/panel.js#L99-L102).\r\n\r\nThat would however broaden the API surface. I think it might be time to create an actual connector interface documenting all these required methods.",
